98b1b9f88958408258fd15340dcec8cf8c6a7","tid":2310364,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T07:59:00.000Z","msg":"警員鄧梓良：「快啲講！再唔講掟你落樓！」鄧繼而開窗，並從後壓着張上半身出窗外<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201203/VRQZ355U5NGJRIDNZOGM6FX24A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201203%2FVRQZ355U5NGJRIDNZOGM6FX24A%2F&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07an0tGPabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=f39fcf7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201203%2FVRQZ355U5NGJRIDNZOGM6FX24A%2F&h=04c3a761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201203/VRQZ355U5NGJRIDNZOGM6FX24A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n辯方：警推被告半身出窗威脅掟落樓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WuSFwWdnxED1dGRlX5l1bkBLg6s=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q27SXHGFIZAWXICQHLV3HWYBSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWuSFwWdnxED1dGRlX5l1bkBLg6s%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ27SXHGFIZAWXICQHLV3HWYBSQ.jpg&h=5842ef46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■涉事警員鄧梓良昨作供後登上私家車離去。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。。。。。開啟窗戶推被告上半身出窗，警告謂：「快啲講！再唔講掟你落樓！」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要求交出手機密碼解鎖<br />\n<br />\n負責警誡張的警員鄧梓良。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。又指鄧帶張入洗手間，要求交出手機密碼，捉住張的手按在其手機，企圖為手機解鎖。惟張拒絕交出密碼，鄧不耐煩謂：<span class=\"orange\">「快啲講！再唔講掟你落樓！」鄧繼而開窗，並從後壓着張上半身出窗外，警告稱：「你望下呢度好高，好容易就掟你落樓。」</span>鄧又對張說：「嗰兩個男仔篤咗你出嚟，你有冇嘢想講？」<br />\n<br />\n辯方又指鄧帶女被告蘇美莉入廁所，捉着她至窗邊說：「生得好眉好貌，點解要做呢啲嘢？」<span class=\"orange\">再推她的上半身出窗外及說：「你今次死梗，你唔死都冇用，不如跳出去。」</span>鄧一律否認。聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC908、918/19"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0262576cf37a17b6cf5f5040df7a7c37e4061441","tid":2310364,"uid":65449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95